```

---

## ⚠️ Important Notes

* FAISS vector files are excluded from GitHub using `.gitignore`
* Embeddings are generated dynamically at runtime
* Some YouTube videos may not have transcripts available

---

## 💡 Key Learnings

* Built an end-to-end RAG system from scratch
* Understood the importance of retrieval quality in LLM systems
* Implemented prompt engineering to reduce hallucinations
* Optimized performance using caching in Streamlit

